WEBVTT

00:00:20.813 --> 00:00:21.688
Fuck.

00:00:28.063 --> 00:00:30.063
Fuck me. You caught two?

00:00:33.438 --> 00:00:35.355
Sir, want to buy a lottery ticket?

00:00:35.438 --> 00:00:38.855
Do I look lucky to you?
I haven't caught a thing.

00:00:38.938 --> 00:00:40.313
Ask someone else.

00:00:42.355 --> 00:00:46.063
Might as well buy one.
Your luck could change.

00:00:47.063 --> 00:00:48.771
See my face?

00:00:49.271 --> 00:00:50.271
Look lucky to you?

00:00:53.438 --> 00:00:57.230
Meeting me was lucky.
I have a powerful amulet.

00:00:57.896 --> 00:01:01.855
Guarantee it'll turn your luck around.

00:01:03.188 --> 00:01:04.605
Keep it for yourself.

00:01:05.730 --> 00:01:06.730
Don't believe me?

00:01:11.021 --> 00:01:11.855
How about this?

00:01:12.438 --> 00:01:16.480
If it doesn't work, you'll be doing me
a favor taking it off my hands.

00:01:16.980 --> 00:01:18.480
But if it does,

00:01:20.146 --> 00:01:21.146
come work for me.

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:23.063
The hell you talking about?

00:01:32.438 --> 00:01:35.396
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:37.188 --> 00:01:41.480
A LIFETIME OF LUCK

00:02:05.355 --> 00:02:07.646
-The demon's coming.
-No riding in the corridor.

00:02:08.730 --> 00:02:09.980
Wang Hsiao-ming!

00:02:10.063 --> 00:02:13.188
-You're supposed to be the adult here.
-He started it, not me.

00:02:13.271 --> 00:02:14.605
It's all your fault.

00:02:15.105 --> 00:02:16.355
You still at it?

00:02:19.188 --> 00:02:21.313
The demon's coming.

00:02:26.063 --> 00:02:28.146
-I'm going.
-Take care.

00:03:04.563 --> 00:03:05.688
Old guard. Delivery.

00:03:07.730 --> 00:03:08.563
Thank you.

00:03:26.896 --> 00:03:28.271
FEITI TEMPLE

00:03:35.313 --> 00:03:37.230
Brother Yu, Silly Chiang is back.

00:03:38.563 --> 00:03:40.730
Brother Yu. Look.

00:03:44.313 --> 00:03:45.230
I'm telling you,

00:03:46.146 --> 00:03:49.146
I'm on such a roll. It's like I'm blessed.

00:03:51.355 --> 00:03:53.813
This lucky amulet
is bringing you good luck.

00:03:56.771 --> 00:04:00.146
Bro, what else can I do now I'm so lucky?

00:04:01.813 --> 00:04:02.855
Chiang.

00:04:03.396 --> 00:04:08.271
With such good luck,
you should be asking what can't you do?

00:04:11.730 --> 00:04:13.438
Right. I'll get going then.

00:04:22.980 --> 00:04:25.730
DONGFENG MARKET

00:04:31.313 --> 00:04:34.730
I told you to hide it properly.
Who's to blame now it's been stolen?

00:04:36.063 --> 00:04:37.521
Damn, it must be Wu Tien-chi.

00:04:39.563 --> 00:04:42.105
He sent someone to steal it
as soon as we found it.

00:04:42.188 --> 00:04:43.105
What does that prove?

00:04:45.355 --> 00:04:46.730
He's desperate.

00:04:47.730 --> 00:04:50.105
Of course he's desperate.

00:04:50.855 --> 00:04:52.230
Did you find the thief yet?

00:04:54.063 --> 00:04:58.063
Su Chih-chiang, aka Silly Chiang.
Prior convictions for gambling and theft.

00:04:58.146 --> 00:05:01.188
Silly enough to leave fingerprints
when he's got a record.

00:05:02.271 --> 00:05:03.188
Got an address?

00:05:12.230 --> 00:05:15.980
I checked the surveillance footage.
He always comes here.

00:05:16.063 --> 00:05:17.230
He loves to gamble.

00:05:27.396 --> 00:05:28.938
Yes, I won again.

00:05:35.063 --> 00:05:35.896
Look.

00:05:36.938 --> 00:05:38.563
I'm winning big time.

00:05:39.230 --> 00:05:41.438
-Why does he always win?
-Look.

00:05:42.063 --> 00:05:43.355
It can't be down to luck.

00:05:44.188 --> 00:05:47.021
Either he's cheating
or he's running some kind of scam.

00:05:51.021 --> 00:05:54.855
Chao says they're already outside.
All the exits are blocked.

00:05:55.688 --> 00:05:56.730
Let's get him.

00:05:56.813 --> 00:05:59.021
It's the jackpot… It's gonna be mine…

00:06:01.438 --> 00:06:02.896
I got it! Look.

00:06:02.980 --> 00:06:05.063
-I hit it big!
-Look, incredible!

00:06:06.063 --> 00:06:07.396
-Police.
-Scram!

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.688
Fuck.

00:06:10.230 --> 00:06:11.313
Trying to run?

00:06:17.230 --> 00:06:18.271
Out of the way!

00:06:25.605 --> 00:06:26.646
-Stop!
-What the heck?

00:06:29.021 --> 00:06:30.105
I'm sorry.

00:06:38.188 --> 00:06:39.063
Come catch me!

00:06:44.813 --> 00:06:46.480
You got a death wish?

00:06:55.521 --> 00:06:57.313
-Where are you going?
-Let go.

00:06:57.396 --> 00:06:59.605
-Where's the incense burner?
-Let go.

00:07:02.771 --> 00:07:03.605
Serves you right.

00:07:07.271 --> 00:07:08.105
Get up…

00:07:10.480 --> 00:07:13.230
Where did you go? Where's Chao?

00:07:13.313 --> 00:07:16.730
Not here. I sent the wrong address.
He really tore me a new one.

00:07:18.271 --> 00:07:21.313
-Fuck.
-Damn it, how are we this unlucky?

00:07:21.813 --> 00:07:24.230
-The stars are against us.
-Or Mercury in retrograde.

00:07:24.313 --> 00:07:27.063
-So what should we do?
-Eat some lucky pork noodles.

00:07:57.896 --> 00:08:00.688
WANG YU-CHING:

00:08:00.771 --> 00:08:03.688
I'M ALMOST THERE
LET'S GRAB A SNACK

00:08:16.563 --> 00:08:18.521
-Hello?
-Mr. Wang.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:21.105
You're the guy from last time.

00:08:21.188 --> 00:08:23.480
You let that thug Hsieh Kun-hao get away.

00:08:23.563 --> 00:08:24.938
The police let him go.

00:08:25.021 --> 00:08:27.855
They said he has nothing to do
with her disappearance

00:08:28.855 --> 00:08:30.480
Why would you believe them?

00:08:32.146 --> 00:08:35.646
They never took this case seriously.

00:08:38.105 --> 00:08:40.980
Your daughter is outside Water Gate No. 7.

00:08:42.063 --> 00:08:43.480
Go now.

00:08:43.563 --> 00:08:45.688
Or it'll be too late.

00:09:04.021 --> 00:09:05.605
-You reported it?
-Yes.

00:09:07.313 --> 00:09:08.480
The body's over there.

00:09:17.105 --> 00:09:17.938
Thanks.

00:09:25.105 --> 00:09:27.313
Chang Min,
this is the info we have so far.

00:09:29.813 --> 00:09:30.646
Chao.

00:09:31.313 --> 00:09:34.938
Jane Doe, about the same age
as Wang Yu-ching.

00:09:35.021 --> 00:09:38.396
But there's no head.
We'll need the DNA analysis to know more.

00:09:39.230 --> 00:09:42.938
-Stop! This is a crime scene.
-Sir! What are you doing?

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:45.146
-Fuck.
-Hey, stop him.

00:09:45.938 --> 00:09:46.855
Mr. Wang.

00:09:48.813 --> 00:09:50.688
-Mr. Wang.
-Is it Ching?

00:09:50.771 --> 00:09:52.771
-She's the same age.
-Tell me. Is it her?

00:09:52.855 --> 00:09:55.730
-But it might not be her.
-Calm down, Mr. Wang.

00:09:55.813 --> 00:09:56.646
Calm down.

00:09:56.730 --> 00:09:58.980
-Is it her?
-We don't know for sure.

00:09:59.063 --> 00:10:00.980
Mr. Wang, calm down first.

00:10:07.646 --> 00:10:09.605
What use are the police?

00:10:11.646 --> 00:10:13.730
Aren't you supposed to catch the bad guys?

00:10:15.438 --> 00:10:18.480
Aren't you supposed to
bring criminals to justice?

00:10:18.563 --> 00:10:20.105
You useless piece of shit!

00:10:20.188 --> 00:10:21.938
You're all useless!

00:10:24.063 --> 00:10:25.938
My daughter's dead because of you.

00:10:27.188 --> 00:10:29.355
She's dead because of you.

00:10:38.188 --> 00:10:39.480
I'm going to kill him.

00:10:40.146 --> 00:10:41.355
I'm going to kill him.

00:10:41.438 --> 00:10:43.396
Damn it. It's all your fault.

00:10:45.063 --> 00:10:46.521
It's all your fault.

00:10:53.730 --> 00:10:56.480
I'm going to kill him!

00:11:04.563 --> 00:11:09.105
Boss, I got the incense burner.
What should I do next?

00:11:09.188 --> 00:11:12.521
Look after it for me.
Don't let Han Chieh find it.

00:11:13.063 --> 00:11:14.438
Okay, got it.

00:11:15.813 --> 00:11:17.021
Also…

00:11:18.313 --> 00:11:19.938
You could…

00:11:21.688 --> 00:11:25.730
Stir things up at Dongfeng Market.
Keep Han Chieh busy for me.

00:11:26.730 --> 00:11:29.313
No problem. That's my area of expertise.

00:11:42.896 --> 00:11:45.605
Hi, Little Leafy. We meet again.

00:11:46.438 --> 00:11:48.480
-Waiting for Chieh?
-Yeah.

00:11:48.563 --> 00:11:52.063
He seems in a pretty bad mood today.
I don't dare go upstairs.

00:11:52.146 --> 00:11:54.855
Oh please, he just likes to act all moody.

00:11:54.938 --> 00:11:57.188
He's a big softie really.

00:11:59.188 --> 00:12:03.480
I used to have a psychopathic sugar daddy
who'd beat me for no reason.

00:12:03.563 --> 00:12:05.771
I couldn't take it,
so I tried to leave him.

00:12:06.688 --> 00:12:11.230
But that psychopath wouldn't let me go.
Chieh helped me deal with him in the end.

00:12:11.313 --> 00:12:12.521
Why aren't you together?

00:12:16.063 --> 00:12:21.146
Things are pretty chill
between us right now. It suits us both.

00:12:32.313 --> 00:12:34.105
Is that a wig you're wearing?

00:12:35.563 --> 00:12:36.605
Yeah.

00:12:37.813 --> 00:12:38.896
From the chemo.

00:12:48.188 --> 00:12:52.271
In all the years I've known Chieh,
I've only ever seen him fall for one girl.

00:12:52.980 --> 00:12:55.355
She was sick like you.

00:12:56.605 --> 00:12:57.521
Huh?

00:12:58.605 --> 00:13:00.146
She was terminally ill.

00:13:00.730 --> 00:13:03.521
You know,
Chieh tried to take his own life.

00:13:03.605 --> 00:13:05.980
She didn't have much time left.

00:13:06.563 --> 00:13:08.980
They both lost hope in life,

00:13:09.563 --> 00:13:11.730
yet still wanted something to hold onto.

00:13:12.563 --> 00:13:15.730
Chieh stayed with her
until her time was up.

00:13:17.271 --> 00:13:22.313
Since then, he's never gotten
seriously involved with another girl.

00:13:23.188 --> 00:13:24.813
He'd rather pay for it.

00:13:26.813 --> 00:13:28.188
It keeps things simpler.

00:13:42.271 --> 00:13:44.146
Wow, look.

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:47.313
Incredible…

00:13:48.271 --> 00:13:51.063
Come on, to us. Cheers.

00:13:51.146 --> 00:13:55.021
A TV, air-con, deck chairs.
I even got a coconut tree for you.

00:13:55.105 --> 00:13:57.813
This isn't hell. It's basically a resort.

00:14:00.188 --> 00:14:03.896
Kid, you've worked hard
to rack up merit with me over the years.

00:14:03.980 --> 00:14:07.688
But you never use it on yourself.
I find that interesting.

00:14:15.938 --> 00:14:17.313
I owe them this.

00:14:18.730 --> 00:14:20.938
Besides, the Demon King's new agent
is tough.

00:14:21.021 --> 00:14:23.230
I'll probably settle down here soon too.

00:14:24.063 --> 00:14:25.146
Settle down, my ass.

00:14:25.230 --> 00:14:26.855
I want you all in on this.

00:14:27.438 --> 00:14:30.896
I didn't choose you
for being young and a good fighter.

00:14:32.063 --> 00:14:33.521
Then why did you choose me?

00:14:35.188 --> 00:14:36.271
Take a guess.

00:14:52.521 --> 00:14:53.355
Han Chieh.

00:14:55.313 --> 00:14:56.646
Why are you here again?

00:14:56.730 --> 00:15:01.271
Mei-na and I are eating with Sister Lo,
then I'm playing games with the old guard.

00:15:02.688 --> 00:15:04.771
-You're keeping busy.
-Yep.

00:15:11.938 --> 00:15:14.396
Everything all right? How are you feeling?

00:15:15.605 --> 00:15:16.688
I'm fine.

00:15:17.188 --> 00:15:19.646
You're the one acting all weird and moody.

00:15:19.730 --> 00:15:23.271
I don't even dare feed Javvy,
in case I annoy you.

00:15:25.105 --> 00:15:26.688
I've got so much going on.

00:15:28.021 --> 00:15:29.355
It's driving me nuts.

00:15:39.813 --> 00:15:40.813
What?

00:15:41.730 --> 00:15:42.813
Han Chieh.

00:15:43.563 --> 00:15:47.063
If I get a boyfriend someday,
I hope he's just like you.

00:15:51.646 --> 00:15:55.730
And I thought you were just an idiot.
Turns out you're an idiot with bad taste.

00:16:02.688 --> 00:16:05.688
Chieh! Someone's causing trouble.
Go and help the old guard.

00:16:09.313 --> 00:16:12.563
How dare you touch my stuff?
I'll kick your ass!

00:16:29.480 --> 00:16:33.146
Chieh, these hooligans
want to have a barbecue on the rooftop.

00:16:33.230 --> 00:16:36.896
They even demanded
that you have a drink with them.

00:16:36.980 --> 00:16:38.605
-I…
-Old guard!

00:16:39.230 --> 00:16:40.105
I…

00:16:43.021 --> 00:16:44.063
A barbecue upstairs?

00:16:44.146 --> 00:16:45.021
FEITI TEMPLE

00:16:45.105 --> 00:16:46.230
You have to defeat me first.

00:16:52.563 --> 00:16:56.230
You're Han Chieh, right?
What've you done to piss off the big man?

00:16:56.313 --> 00:16:57.313
The big man?

00:16:57.396 --> 00:17:00.896
I don't usually piss off any big men,
just scumbags down below.

00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:02.021
Finish him.

00:17:12.063 --> 00:17:13.438
Wang Hsiao-ming!

00:17:16.313 --> 00:17:18.355
-What?
-What are you doing?

00:17:18.438 --> 00:17:20.230
What the fuck? Are you blind?

00:17:20.313 --> 00:17:22.021
-What? It wasn't me.
-Fuck you.

00:17:22.105 --> 00:17:25.105
Granny said this is our turf
and I should scare them off.

00:17:25.188 --> 00:17:27.313
-She'll take responsibility.
-How?

00:17:27.396 --> 00:17:28.730
I'll get back to it.

00:17:30.855 --> 00:17:32.063
Not again!

00:17:34.646 --> 00:17:35.521
Damn you.

00:17:37.938 --> 00:17:39.855
-Old guard.
-Little punk.

00:17:39.938 --> 00:17:42.188
What the hell? Fuck.

00:17:43.063 --> 00:17:45.230
-What the hell?
-Kill him!

00:17:45.313 --> 00:17:46.396
Charge!

00:17:46.480 --> 00:17:48.355
-Naughty boys.
-Dare show up here?

00:17:48.438 --> 00:17:51.396
Don't run. Come here.
I'm going to kill you.

00:17:54.896 --> 00:17:56.896
Enough… Stop hitting me…

00:17:58.313 --> 00:18:01.230
Take this! And this!

00:18:03.396 --> 00:18:05.688
I've got you. Can't run now.

00:18:05.771 --> 00:18:07.980
-Just you try.
-You won't get away.

00:18:08.063 --> 00:18:09.313
What do you want?

00:18:09.396 --> 00:18:10.938
Who sent you here?

00:18:11.021 --> 00:18:13.855
Are you stupid?
I wouldn't tell you even if I knew.

00:18:13.938 --> 00:18:15.855
What an embarrassment.

00:18:15.938 --> 00:18:16.813
Let's go!

00:18:17.813 --> 00:18:18.688
Come on.

00:18:20.396 --> 00:18:22.021
Get lost!

00:18:24.938 --> 00:18:28.230
-Look at them run.
-Don't you dare come back.

00:18:39.688 --> 00:18:43.605
-What? Haven't you done enough fighting?
-There's another one, one more.

00:18:46.396 --> 00:18:48.271
Haven't you taken enough?

00:18:48.355 --> 00:18:49.605
Okay… Right away…

00:18:49.688 --> 00:18:50.605
Hurry up.

00:18:56.105 --> 00:18:57.188
What happened?

00:18:58.313 --> 00:18:59.938
Some troublemakers turned up.

00:19:00.688 --> 00:19:01.730
Why are you here?

00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:04.438
We found a Jane Doe this morning.

00:19:04.521 --> 00:19:06.688
Age and appearance match Wang Yu-ching.

00:19:07.438 --> 00:19:08.313
Is it her?

00:19:08.396 --> 00:19:10.855
Not sure yet.
We're waiting for the DNA report.

00:19:10.938 --> 00:19:15.480
But if it is her, then the final sacrifice
for the array must be someone else.

00:19:15.563 --> 00:19:18.146
The full moon is in three days.
What should we do?

00:19:19.230 --> 00:19:21.730
-One more.
-Think they can mess with us? No chance.

00:19:21.813 --> 00:19:24.188
Humans and ghosts
are united in Dongfeng Market.

00:19:24.271 --> 00:19:28.188
We sent those punks packing in no time.

00:19:30.105 --> 00:19:33.355
The magic array was complete,
but he was waiting

00:19:33.438 --> 00:19:36.146
for midnight
when the moon is at its height.

00:19:36.230 --> 00:19:39.646
Only then could he regain his full power
through the array portal.

00:19:39.730 --> 00:19:41.188
Where's the portal?

00:19:41.938 --> 00:19:43.605
At the center of the array,

00:19:44.605 --> 00:19:45.521
Dongfeng Market.

00:19:47.271 --> 00:19:49.438
-The other side…
-The other side? Okay…

00:19:49.521 --> 00:19:52.146
Better not think of coming back
while we're here.

00:19:55.188 --> 00:19:57.021
-Harder.
-The back too…

00:19:57.105 --> 00:19:57.980
The back.

00:20:00.146 --> 00:20:01.938
-Harder.
-That's it, squeeze…

00:20:04.646 --> 00:20:05.480
Everyone.

00:20:10.521 --> 00:20:13.730
I wanted to tell you individually,
but since you're all here,

00:20:14.980 --> 00:20:16.605
I may as well tell you all.

00:20:23.896 --> 00:20:27.605
A demon is coming for me
and coming for Dongfeng Market.

00:20:28.813 --> 00:20:33.105
For everyone's safety, I want you
to leave Dongfeng Market for a while.

00:20:35.855 --> 00:20:38.146
I'll stay and protect
the ghosts who can't leave.

00:20:41.396 --> 00:20:44.355
You want us to go
and leave you here all by yourself?

00:20:45.438 --> 00:20:47.980
I'm the Third Crown Prince's agent.
I have to stay.

00:20:51.980 --> 00:20:53.355
If I defeat him,

00:20:54.813 --> 00:20:55.938
you can all come back.

00:20:57.146 --> 00:20:58.396
But even if I lose,

00:21:00.230 --> 00:21:01.855
there's no need to worry.

00:21:02.813 --> 00:21:04.396
Another agent will handle it.

00:21:13.771 --> 00:21:15.021
Han Chieh.

00:21:15.105 --> 00:21:17.563
-Wait…
-What should we do?

00:21:17.688 --> 00:21:19.521
-This is our home.
-We can't leave.

00:21:19.605 --> 00:21:21.396
-Where can we go?
-He wants us gone.

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:23.188
I'm not going anywhere.

00:21:23.271 --> 00:21:26.355
-I'll die without the internet.
-Aren't you already dead?

00:21:27.813 --> 00:21:32.355
CORPSELORDS WILL RISE
AND ATTACK AT FULL MOON

00:21:48.230 --> 00:21:49.188
What?

00:21:56.021 --> 00:21:58.771
You've really upset them this time.

00:22:01.730 --> 00:22:03.938
What would your parents think
if they knew?

00:22:05.355 --> 00:22:06.355
My parents?

00:22:08.688 --> 00:22:10.188
They're in hell because of me.

00:22:11.605 --> 00:22:13.146
I'm still atoning for my sins.

00:22:14.938 --> 00:22:16.271
It's been over ten years.

00:22:18.021 --> 00:22:21.896
The more it hurts after completing a task,
the better I feel.

00:22:24.771 --> 00:22:26.105
At least I can sleep.

00:22:34.063 --> 00:22:35.813
Do you think my dad was a bad judge?

00:22:38.980 --> 00:22:42.521
Sure. Based on the verdict
in Wu Tien-chi's trial, he probably was.

00:22:43.438 --> 00:22:46.105
But that isn't the way I remember him.

00:22:47.271 --> 00:22:50.730
He took his job seriously
and handled every case with care.

00:22:51.313 --> 00:22:53.396
He demanded perfection from himself.

00:22:54.813 --> 00:22:56.605
But judges are human, not gods.

00:22:57.188 --> 00:23:00.938
He buckled under the pressure
and gave Wu Tien-chi a light sentence.

